Package com.gmail.aydinov.sergey.simple_debugger_plugin.processor

package com.gmail.aydinov.sergey.simple_debugger_plugin.processor
Event processing components of the Simple Debugger Plugin.

This package contains classes responsible for collecting, queuing, and processing debugger-related events. These components form the processing pipeline that connects event producers (core logic, UI, handlers) with event consumers, ensuring ordered and controlled handling of debugger events.

The processors in this package help to separate event production from event consumption, improving modularity and simplifying coordination between different parts of the debugger.

Author: Sergei Aidinov
Email: sergey.aydinov@gmail.com
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/sergei-aydinov/
